### Exported Reports API Tests
### Requires Firebase authentication token

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001
@accountId = 1
@token = YOUR_FIREBASE_TOKEN_HERE

### Get all exported reports (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/{{accountId}}/exported-reports?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get unresolved reports only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/{{accountId}}/exported-reports?unresolvedOnly=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get reports with date filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/{{accountId}}/exported-reports?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get a specific exported report
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/{{accountId}}/exported-reports/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create a new exported report
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/{{accountId}}/exported-reports
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "report": "This is the full report content exported from the PACS system...",
  "reportDateTime": "2025-01-22T14:30:00Z"
}

### Mark a report as resolved
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/{{accountId}}/exported-reports/1/resolve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get exported reports statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/{{accountId}}/exported-reports/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete an exported report
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/{{accountId}}/exported-reports/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/{{accountId}}/exported-reports?page=2&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test with invalid account (should return 403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/999/exported-reports
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test without authentication (should return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/{{accountId}}/exported-reports
